{"tid":1580446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國 [到底有冇] 正式定義粵語為一種語言？","createTime":"2019-09-19T05:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T11:16:11.000Z","uid":258970,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"308e87ba1683f0074c085181c71803c73affce66","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:35:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\">呢篇Medium文章將會解答各位疑難:</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&ldquo;十個香港人十個都唔知道嘅 4 個廣東話歷史常識&rdquo; by 阿擇 （Chaaak） </span><a href=\"https://link.medium.com/moiZn68m6Z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.medium.com%2FmoiZn68m6Z&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5Qb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=7ea7240c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.medium.com/moiZn68m6Z</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">//要保護一隻語言，其實唔使堆砌幾百個理由，亦都唔使踩低其他語言去抬高自己。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">//你鍾意自己嘅語言文化，就應該去保護，唔使嘥時間去幫自己辯解。你去醫院睇病你使唔使證明自己對社會有價值，說服個醫生去救你？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">//希望各位粵語人喺保護自己語言嘅時候，要有返啲正確認識，唔好做無謂嘅爭拗。同時要避免用錯資料，免得俾人喺啲旁枝末節捉到痛腳</span>"},{"pid":"e63fa21976013a82f892a69d15888f3fb15b9eb5","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"276424ca2589d1bcd7b77edf8d26670b71283e9b","tid":1580446,"uid":54014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"幫你推一次"},{"pid":"79a1521ebb21fd79d6aa982c8720497621c445bc","tid":1580446,"uid":56726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推"},{"pid":"77305e9619e3a82b1ed1c1d395c193e259036f23","tid":1580446,"uid":259901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:18:56.000Z","msg":"粵語係語言學分類等級上同普通話係一個level<br />\n<br />\n既係<br />\n如果話普通話係語言，咁粵語都係語言，兩者同時under「漢語」呢個大group<br />\n如果話普通話係方言，咁粵語都係方言，兩個都係「漢語」呢個語言嘅方言<br />\n<br />\n咩福建話閩南話上海話一樣，都係呢個分法<br />\n所以聯合國官方語言係「漢語」，唔係「普通話」<br />\n大陸人講嘅只係「普通話」"},{"pid":"13e045113d46eca0e45a2cd02ee2f7d4904fa42e","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"見facebook已經有人援引所謂&ldquo;聯合國&rdquo;講法<br />\n自推十次"},{"pid":"666574577a9ea6c4b728f9fd1913bffab7301ff3","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0eaf06e45e085c7e04c8afe2d3ab6ab4fdbeaae7","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad992ea309083d06c67987e01aaf170233e59beb","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:08:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"462654550707053479eb0c835c326a24a7d1fc0a","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:10:39.000Z","msg":"繼續"},{"pid":"5d25a723cea1a8de42feec783da5740165da7365","tid":1580446,"uid":258970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T11:16:11.000Z","msg":"請問而家係咪冇得自推？<br />\n推極都見唔到自己個post有上水嘅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}